Feature: View Tutorial
    As a first time user of TaskIt, I want to see a tutorial on how to use the system, so that I can learn how to use the system.

    Background:
        Given The user "<email>" luke.skywalker@rebellion.com exists

    Scenario Outline: Sucessfully view tutorial after first login (normal flow)
        Given The user status "<has_seen_tutorial>" for user "<email>" is "false"
        When The user "<email>" logs in with password "<password>"
        Then The user status "<has_seen_tutorial>" for user "<email>" shall be "true"

        Examples:
            | email                        | password      | has_seen_tutorial |
            | luke.skywalker@rebellion.com | jediknight457 | true              |

    Scenario Outline: Attempt to watch tutorial after next login (error flow)
        Given The user status "<has_seen_tutorial>" for user "<email>" is "true"
        When The user "<email>" logs in with password "<password>"
        Then The user status "<has_seen_tutorial>" for user "<email>" shall be "true"

        Examples:
            | email                        | password      | has_seen_tutorial |
            | luke.skywalker@rebellion.com | jediknight457 | true              |

